examples.en: He has been tripping for three weeks.
He received a two-minute penalty for tripping.
She walked with a light tripping step.
He was very glad when he found an author tripping.
She had dropped some LSD and had been tripping for an unknown number of hours.
My basset hound is always tripping over her long, floppy ears.
When tripping through the Yukon take some time to explore our museums.
